PROBLEM: Query the difference between the maximum and minimum populations in CITY.
****************

+-------------+------------+
| Field       |   Type     |
+-------------+------------+
| ID          | NUMBER     |
| NAME        | VARCHAR2   |
| COUNTRYCODE | VARCHAR2   |
| DISTRICT    | VARCHAR2   |
| POPULATION  | NUMBER     |
+-------------+------------+


Select Max(POPULATION) - Min(POPULATION) From CITY


